==Eat== [[File:Herttoniemi Manor House (Herttoniemen kartano).jpg|thumbnail|Herttoniemi Manor, nowadays both a sight and perhaps the suburbs' finest restaurant ]] ===Budget=== There are plenty of fast food joints in the area, both McDonald's and its Finnish competitor have a few places here. You usually don't have to travel far to find some place making pizza or kebabs which can be enjoyed with a soft drink or a beer for under €10. * {{eat | name=Itis Kebab | alt= | url= | email= | address=Turunlinnantie 12 | lat=60.21080 | long=25.07949 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content= }} * {{eat | name=Hungry Hub Vuosaari | alt= | url=https://hungryhub.fi/home | email= | address=Vuotie 47 B | lat=60.2068 | long=25.1477 | directions= | phone=+358 44 246 6970 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M–Th 10:00–22:00, F 10:00–23:00, Sa 11:00–23:00, Su 11:00–22:00 | price= | content=A fast food restaurant. }} * {{eat | name=King Kebab Herttoniemi| alt= | url=https://www.kingkebab.fi/ | email= | address=Sahaajankatu 43, Herttoniemi | lat=60.2059 | long=25.0528 | directions=at the Atlas Tower | phone=+358 44 984 4073 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=A fast food restaurant. }} * {{eat | name=Kontulan Pizza & Kebab | alt= | url=http://www.kontulankebabpizza.fi/ | email= | address=Kontula mall | lat=60.23678 | long=25.08208 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content= }} * {{eat | name=Myllyn murkina | alt= | url=https://www.hangonry.fi/hankkeet/ | email= | address=Jauhokuja 1-3 | lat=60.224549 | long=25.078032 | directions=at Liikuntamylly Myllypuro | phone=+358 44 986 2969 | tollfree= | hours=M-F 11:00-15:00 | price=Lunch €5 | lastedit=2023-01-15 | content= }} * {{eat | name=Pit Stop Pizzeria | alt= | url= | email= | address=Rödje-Fantsin tie 2 | lat=60.2514 | long=25.1725 | directions=in Östersundom | phone=+358 9 790009 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M–Th 10:00–21:00, F 10:00–22:00, Weekend 11:00–22:00 | price= | content= }} * {{eat | name=Royal Namaskaar | alt= | url=https://royalnamaskaar.fi/ | email= | address=Sahaajankatu 31 | lat=60.2046 | long=25.0510 | directions= | phone=+358 50 522 5800 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=An Indian restaurant. }} * {{eat | name=Southland | alt= | url= | email= | address=Meri-Rastilantie 3 C (''M Rastila'') | lat=60.203961 | long=25.117176 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2018-06-14 | content=Quite standard Westernized Chinese fare, but unbeatable value for money in Helsinki, as most dishes only set you back €7-8, even during dinner time. }} * {{eat | name=Waste&Feast Snellu Cafe | alt= | url=http://www.wastefeast.eu/ravintolat/snellu-cafe/ | email= | address=Turunlinnantie 3 | lat=60.211463 | long=25.079444 | directions=Matteuksenkirkko | phone= | tollfree= | hours=11:00-13:00 | price=Main €2, dessert €1 | lastedit=2021-06-20 | content=Prepares meals from store surplus dishes. }}
===Mid-range=== Like most cities, suburbs aren't the place to find an abundance of restaurants. Your choice in the mid-range section are pretty much the restaurants of the shopping malls, some pubs that happen to serve food plus the ordinary Chinese, Thai and Middle Eastern restaurants which might be very good value for your money.
[[File:Buffet lunch at restaurant Fregatti.jpg|thumb|right|Ravintola Fregatti serves buffet lunch on weekdays and Saturdays.]] * {{eat | name=Bar Taikurin Hattu | alt= | url= | email= | address=Tanhuantie 3 |lat=60.23558 | long=25.09268 | directions=in Kontula | phone=+358 40 195 6686 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M-Th 13:00-00:00, F 13:00-02:00, Sa 11:00-02:00, Su 11:00-00:00 | price= | content= }} * {{eat | name=Fornitaly | alt= | url= | email= | address=Jollaksentie 54 B | lat=60.1638 | long=25.0810 | directions=in Jollas | phone=+358 40 469 2258 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=F 16:00–20:00, Weekend 13:00–19:00 | price= | content=A pizzeria. }} * {{eat | name=The Bro's Burger | alt= | url=https://www.thebrosburger.fi/ | email=liem.nguyen@thebrosburger.fi | address=Kirvesmiehenkatu 2 | lat=60.1929 | long=25.0401 | directions=in Herttoniemi | phone=+358 50 552 5887 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M–Th 10:00–22:00, F–Sa 10:00–23:00, Su 11:00–20:00 | price= | content= }} * {{eat | name=Ravintola Fregatti | alt= | url=http://www.ravintolafregatti.fi/ | email= | address=Valkopaadentie 1 |lat=60.20653 | long=25.14537 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M-Th 10:00-23:00, F Sa 10:00-00:00, Su 11:00-22:00 | price= | content= }} * {{eat | name=Rastilan Kartano | alt= | url=https://cafemonami.fi/ | email= | address=Karavaanikatu 4 | lat=60.20758 | long=25.11825 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content= }} * {{eat | name=Ravintola Gurkha | alt= | url=http://www.gurkha.fi/ | email= | address=Hiihtäjäntie 7 | lat=60.19483 | long=25.02882| directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=Nepalese restaurant. }} * {{eat | name=Il Treno | alt= | url=http://www.iltreno.fi/ | email= | address=Pallaksentie 4 | lat=60.23850 | long=25.11004 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content= }} * {{eat | name=Martisor Ravintola | alt= | url=https://www.martisor.fi/ | email=ravintola.martisor@gmail.com | address=Retkeilijänkatu 11 |lat=60.2051 | long=25.1252 | directions=in Rastila; near the camping area | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=A Somalian restaurant. }} * {{eat | name=Mandraki | alt= | url= | email=mandraki.helsinki@gmail.com | address=Laivalahden puistotie 7 LT 5 | lat=60.1881 | long=25.0312 | directions=in Herttoniemi | phone=+358 45 103 7137 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M–F 11:00–21:00, Sa 12:00–22:00, Su 12:00–18:00 | price=€15–20 | content=A Greek restaurant. }} * {{eat | name=Ristorante Momento | alt= | url= | email= | address=Itäkatu 1 |lat=60.21098 | long=25.08071 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content= }} * {{eat | name=Suola & Pippuri | alt= | url=http://suolajapippuri.fi/ | email= | address=Itäkatu 1-7 (''M Itäkeskus'') | lat=60.213496 | long=25.085238 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2018-06-14 | content=Offering unpretentious Finnish fare, probably one of the best options inside shopping centre Itis if you're hungry. }} * {{eat | name=Thai Orchid Itis | alt= | url=http://www.thaimaalainenravintola.fi/itis | email= | address=Itäkatu 1-7 (''M Itäkeskus'') | lat=60.213496 | long=25.085238 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2018-06-14 | content=Offers an excellent and authentic Thai buffet (including decent sushi) during lunchtime inside shopping centre Itis. }}
===Splurge=== * {{eat | name=Wanha Mylly | alt= | url=http://www.vanhamylly.fi | email= | address=Linnanrakentajantie 12 but Johan Sederholmintie 8 (behind the building) if you need to park your car | lat=60.19039 | long=25.04180 | directions=in Herttoniemi district | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M 11:00-21:00, Tu-F 11:00-22:00, Sa 12:00-22:00, Su 12:00-21:00 | price=mains €20-40, 3-course menu €50-70 | content=Casual fine dining in the former Herttoniemi manor. Specializes in steaks, with the large Lankkupihvi steak served on a wooden platter as the house special. Extensive wine list which you wouldn't expect to find in this part of Helsinki. In the summer you can enjoy your meal in the outdoor garden if you like. }} * {{eat | name=Kulosaaren Casino | alt= | url=http://www.kulosaarencasino.fi/en | email= | address=Hopeasalmenpolku 1 | lat=60.18082 | long=25.00642 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M-F 17:00-00:00 | price= | content=Hosted in the old casino on Kulosaari, this restaurant is your second alternative if you want to have a finer meal. Popular among diplomats, as many embassies are located on Kulosaari island. }}
