 a good selection of beers and ciders. Often hosts entertainment nights with pub quizzes, live music or stand-up comedy. }} * {{drink | name=Wanha Rouva | alt= | url= | email= | address=Ostostie 4 | lat=60.23761 | long=25.08336 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content= }} * {{drink | name=Svenkka | alt= | url=http://www.puotilankartano.fi/1_3_svenkka.html | email= | address=Puotilantie 7 (''M Puotila'') | lat=60.212241 | long=25.106815 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2018-06-14 | content=Located on the grounds of Puotila Manor, has a nice terrace to enjoy a pint on a warm summer's day. }}
