0832| directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours=Su–Th 09:00–02:00, F Sa 09:00-03:00 | price= | content= }} * {{drink | name=Teeritupa | alt= | url= | email= | address=Pekanraitti 4 | lat=60.25221 | long=25.02053 | directions=in Malmi | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours=Daily 09:00–22:00 | price= | content=A pub. }}
==Sleep== Northern Helsinki is likely the least touristy part of the city but does have a couple of hotels, moreover Airbnb accommodation may be available if you wish to stay overnight here. For a bigger selection of official hotels, head to [[Helsinki#Districts|another district]] or to Vantaa.
* {{sleep | name=Noli Malmi | alt= | url=https://nolistudios.com/en/noli-malmi-helsinki | email=malmi@nolistudios.com | address=Vanha Helsingintie 19 | lat=60.2491 | long=25.0096 | directions=in Malmi district; near the railway station | phone=+358 20-144-1054 | tollfree= | fax= | checkin= | checkout= | price= | content= }} * {{sleep | name=Best Western Hotel Haaga | alt= | url=http://www.bestwestern.fi/etsi_hotelli/hotel_haaga_helsinki.213.xhtml {{dead link|December 2020}} | email=hotel@haaga.fi | address=Nuijamiestentie 10 | lat=60.21804 | long=24.90705 | directions=in Haaga district of Helsinki | phone=+358 9 580-7877 | tollfree= | fax=+358 9 5807 8386 | checkin= | checkout= | price= | content= }} * {{sleep | name=Arkadia Hotel & Hostel| alt= | url=http://www.arkadiahotel.fi/en/index.html| email=info@arkadiahotel.fi | address=Tattarisuontie 1 | lat=60.2592 | long=25.0628 | directions= | phone=+358 400-218-748 | tollfree= | fax= | checkin= | checkout= | price=dorm bed €30, rooms from €70 | wikipedia= | wikidata= | lastedit=2018-07-28 | content=This hotel in the Tattarisuo industrial area is likely the only one in the north-eastern corner of Helsinki proper. You can choose between dorm accommodation or private room. The hotel has ample parking space, free Wi-Fi, TVs in the rooms and some rooms have their own bathrooms. }}
