==Eat== ===Budget=== [[File:Visit-suomi-2009-05-by-RalfR-076.jpg|thumbnail|Former Kahvila Suomi, which now goes by the name Kamome, is very popular with Japanese visitors]]
* {{eat | name=Bar No 9 | alt= | url=http://www.bar9.net/ | email= | address=Uudenmaankatu 9 | lat= 60.16493 | long= 24.94177 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=Popular bar that also serves a variety of dishes with a twist of cross-kitchen style, priced from €4.90-15.90, most main courses under €10. Tends to be packed at lunch and dinner time. }} * {{eat | name=Event Arena Bank | alt= | url=http://www.ravintolabank.fi/en/front-page/ | email= | address=Unioninkatu 20 | lat=60.16619 | long=24.95099 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=Free flow lunch restaurant that offers a spacious and luminous environment to spend the lunch hour. The daily Lunch Club menu consists of four different choices all for €9.20. There is choice of Scandinavian style home-cooking, Mediterranean or Asian delicacies, salad bar and soup of the day or vegetarian meal. }} * {{eat | name=Fredan Murkina | alt= | url=https://www.facebook.com/fredanmurkina | email= | address=Fredrikinkatu 16 | lat= 60.161543 | long= 24.940826 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours=Open M–F lunch time, closed around midsummer. | price= | content=Very simple and inexpensive lunch place, no gourmet-stuff going on here, but the sort of food Finns eat at home made fresh on site. Run by a friendly husband and wife team, this kiosk/restaurant melange a stone's throw away from five corners serves one of the cheapest healthy warm lunches you can eat in central Helsinki. Take away also possible if the few tables are full. Soup €4.50, lunch of the day was €5.70 or €7 depending on portion size (Sep 2015). }} * {{eat | name=Ravintola Kamome | alt=former Kahvila Suomi | url=http://www.kamome.fi/food-drink/ | email= | address=Pursimiehenkatu 12 | lat= 60.15955 | long= 24.93865 | directions= | phone=+358 9 657-422 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= M–F till 21:00 | price= | lastedit=2017-12 | content=The Japanese tourists come because the cult hit movie ''Kamome Shokudo'' was filmed here! Japanese cuisine. }} * {{eat | name=Surgical Hospital Restaurant | alt=Kirurgisen sairaalan lounasravintola | url=https://menu.hus.fi/AromieMenus/EN/Default/HUS/KirraLo/Restaurant.aspx | email=ruokapalvelut.meilahti@hus.fi | address=Kasarmikatu 11-13 | lat=60.162175 | long=24.946336 | directions= | phone=+358 50 427 1431 | tollfree= | hours=M–F 10:30–13:30 | price= | lastedit=2022-06-08 | content= }} * {{eat | name=Behnford's | alt= | url=https://www.behnfords.fi/ | email=store@behnfords.fi | address=Bulevardi 22 | lat= 60.1644 | long= 24.9377 | directions=Punavuori | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=British and American store selling food, drinks, candies and other stuff. }}
===Mid-range=== [[File:Steaks of Baltic herring at restaurant Sea Horse, Helsinki, Finland.jpg|thumb|right|Steaks of Baltic herring]] [[File:German-style sausages at restaurant Rymy-Eetu.jpg|thumb|right|German-style sausages]]
* {{eat | name=Adlerfelt | alt= | url=https://adlerfelt.fi/en/ | email= | address=Suomenlinna B 1 | lat= 60.14457 | long= 24.98635 | directions=in the middle of the Suomenlinna Island; near the Ehrensvärd Museum | phone=+358 41-317-0998 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=A restaurant (housed in a magnificent 250-year-old building) with cool Nordic food, interesting drinks and good moments. }} * {{eat | name=Central | alt= | url=http://www.central.fi | email=helsinki.central@restel.fi | address=Pietarinkatu 15 | lat=60.15728 | long=24.94672 | directions= | phone=+358 9 636-483 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=12:00–23:00 mostly | price=Main courses €16-33 | lastedit=2015-10-22 | content=One of the oldest restaurants in Helsinki, dating back to the 1890s. It has been in its current location since the 1960s. Serves a wide variety of common restaurant fare in Finland: salads, pastas, steaks and hamburgers. }} * {{eat | name=Elm | alt= | url=https://www.restaurantelm.fi | email=varaukset@restaurantelm.fi | address=Puistokatu 4 | lat=60.15701 | long=24.95252 | directions=near the Kaivopuisto park | phone=+358 400-414-105 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M–Th 11:30–14:30 & 17:00–22:00, F 11:30–14:30 & 17:00–23:00, Sa 13:00–23:00 | price=Lunch €13-16, main courses €12-36 Menu Elm €42 | content=Mediterranean restaurant, serving food made with fresh and authentic ingredients. }} * {{eat | name=Gastone | alt= | url=http://www.gastone.fi | email= | address=Korkeavuorenkatu 45 | lat= 60.16662 | long=24.94603 | directions= | phone=+358 9 666-116 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=Nice restaurant with an Italian flavour. Reservations suggested, particularly on the weekend. }} * {{eat | name=Juuri | alt= | url=http://www.juuri.fi | email= | address=Korkeavuorenkatu 27 | lat=60.16397 | long=24.94628 | directions= | phone=+358 9 635-732 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M–F 11:00–14:00 (lunch) & 16:00–22:00 (à la carte), Sa 12:00–22:00, Su 16:00–22:00 | price=All ''sapakset'' €4.3, main dishes €24, lunch sets €7.5–10 | content=Tiny restaurant known for its special Finnish entrées called ''sapakset'' (a play on ''tapas''), with roots in Finnish food tradition. Try the cabbage roll with crayfish or the egg cheese with marjoram. }} * {{eat | name=Monal | alt= | url=http://ravintolamonal.fi | email=info@ravintolamonal.fi | address=Annankatu 4 | lat=60.1631 | long=24.9422 | directions=close by Kamppi | phone=+358 50-596-9316 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M–F 10:30–22:00, Sa 12:00–22:00, Su 12:00–20:00 | price=Lunch €10, main dishes €15–20 | lastedit=2018-02-10 | content=The restaurant provides excellent hospitality and a wide variety of authentic Indian cuisine. An affordable and changing lunch buffet, dinner, delicious Indian desserts, take away service and catering for smaller or larger events. Peaceful location. }} * {{eat | name=Nikolai | alt= | url=https://kp-ravintolat.fi/en/ | email=tony.hellstrom@gmail.com | address=Suomenlinna A 10 | lat= 60.13888 | long= 24.98924 | directions=in the southern part of the Suomenlinna Island | phone=+358 50-572-6741 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=A pizzeria where you can choose a table either in the labyrinthine fortress ramparts or on the sunny summertime terrace. }} * {{eat | name=Rioni | alt= | url=https://www.rioni.fi/helsinki | email=helsinki@rioni.fi | address=Kasarmikatu 25 | lat=60.16664 | long=24.94786 | directions=near the Esplanadi Park | phone=+358 50-551-2264 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M–Th 13:00–23:00, F–Sa 13:00–00:00, Su 13:00–22:00 | price= | content=A Georgian restaurant serving authentic food. }} * {{eat | name=Rymy-Eetu | alt= | url=http://rymy-eetu.fi | email=ravintola@rymy-eetu.fi | address=Erottaja 15 | lat=60.16609 | long=24.94414 | directions= | phone=+358 40-358-0585 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=Mostly 17:00–03:00 | price=Main courses €13–30 | lastedit=2015-12-09 | content=A German restaurant inspired by the famous ''Hofbräuhaus am Platzl'' in Munich. Spacious, with premises on two floors. Authentic-looking Bavarian-style decor reminiscent of the original ''Hofbräuhaus''. Tasty Bavarian cuisine dishes with copious amounts of meat, but vegetarian options also available. One of the few places in Finland to serve Austro-Bavarian schnitzels of veal rather than pork. A good variety of German beers on tap. }} * {{eat | name=Salve | alt= | url=https://www.raflaamo.fi/en/restaurant/helsinki/salve | email= | address=Hietalahdenranta 5 C | lat=60.16128 | long=24.92991 | directions=in Hietalahti; near S-market | phone=+358 10-766-4280 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M–F 11:00–23:00, Weekend 12:00–23:00 | price= | content=The restaurant's history began in 1897 with a former small kiosk, the door of which sold food and tobacco mainly to sailors. Even today, the restaurant is famous for its Baltic herring dishes. }} * {{eat | name=Same Same – But Different | alt= | url=https://en.samesame.fi | email=email@samesame.fi | address=Tehtaankatu 25 | lat=60.15794 | long=24.93539 | directions=in Punavuori | phone=+358 40-664-8868 | tollfree= | hours=Mostly 11:00–22:00, Su closed | price= | lastedit=2024-08-02 | content=A trendy Asian cuisine restaurant. }} * {{eat | name=Cafe Samovarbar | alt= | url=http://lelumuseo.fi/toymuseum/ | email= | address=Suomenlinna C66 | lat=60.145779 | long=24.991578 | directions=east side of Suomenlinna, follow signs to Toy Museum from the main path | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours=11:00–17:00 | price= | lastedit=2017-09-27 | content=Lovely cafe in the toy museum with proper espresso, ice cream, local snacks and wines, with a terrace overlooking the sea. }} * {{eat | name=Scolare | alt= | url=https://scolare.fi/en/ | email=info@scolare.fi | address=Fabianinkatu 19 | lat=60.16577 | long= 24.94982 | directions= | phone=+358 10-341-9830 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=An Italian restaurant. }} * {{eat | name=Sea Horse | alt= | url=http://www.seahorse.fi | email= | address=Kapteeninkatu 11 | lat=60.15852 | long=24.94642 | directions= | phone=+358 9 628-169 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price=Meals €10-30. | content=Established in 1933 as a basic eatery, this joint has slowly become a local legend affectionately known as ''Sikala'' ("Pigsty"), and both the decor and the menu are still preserved from the 1950s. A long-time ''Wallpaper Magazine'' favourite. Try the famous herring dishes or the onion steak. }} * {{eat | name=Tamarin | alt= | url=http://www.tamarin.fi | email= | address=Iso Roobertinkatu 18, Fredrikinkatu 49, Eteläesplanadi 4 | lat= 60.16355 | long= 24.94273 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price=Main dishes around €14, lunch buffet €8.50 | content=Tasty Thai food. }} * {{eat | name=The Tart | alt= | url=https://www.quandoo.fi/en/place/the-tart-108248 | email= | address=Yrjönkatu 2 | lat=60.163496 | long=24.944909 | directions= | phone=+358 44 902 9024 | tollfree= | hours= | price= main courses around €20 | lastedit=2025-10-04 | content=A British restaurant bar. }} * {{eat | name=Valimo | alt= | url=https://www.valimo.org | email=info@valimo.org | address=Suomenlinna B 13 | lat= 60.14593 | long= 24.98243 | directions= | phone=+358 50-375-2105 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=This café-restaurant is a popular lunch and evening spot for both yachtspeople and the residents of Suomenlinna Island. }} * {{eat | name=Zucchini | alt= | url= | email= | address=Fabianinkatu 4 | lat=60.16596 | long= 24.94947 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= M–F 11:00–16:00 (lunch served the whole time). | price= | content=Cosy vegetarian lunch restaurant with a daily changing soup and main dish (around €9). }}
===Splurge=== [[File:Ravintola Olo (14152999986).jpg|thumbnail|Filet of veal, cabbage, turnip and veal consommé with fermented black currant]]
* {{eat | name=Boathouse | alt= | url= | email=boathouse@kampgroup.fi | address=Liuskasaari island | lat=60.150833 | long=24.948333 | directions= | phone=+358 9 5840-9603 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=May–Sep | price= | content=On Liuskasaari island, Boathouse offers seasonal kitchen and a wide selection of wines. }} * {{eat | name=Demo | alt= | url=http://www.restaurantdemo.fi | email= | address=Uudenmaankatu 9-11 | lat=60.16484 | long=24.94150 | directions= | phone=+358 9 2289-0480 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=An unusual high-class restaurant geared towards the young and trendy, Demo's decor is minimalistic, but the food is of excellent calibre. There are no menus, only set courses pre-chosen based on what is fresh and available for the evening. Easily deserving of its Michelin star. Reservations essential. }} * {{eat | name=Gaijin | alt= | url=http://www.gaijin.fi | email=info@gaijin.fi | address=Bulevardi 6 | lat=60.16597 | long=24.94217 | directions= | phone=+358 10-322-9386 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=17:00-00:00 | price=Main courses €26-42, tasting menus €62-66 | lastedit=2016-07-19 | content=One of Helsinki's finest Asian cuisine restaurants, serving a mixture of Japanese, Chinese and Korean cuisine. Famous for its tasting menus. As the restaurant is very popular and a bit cramped, prior reservations are recommended, although not mandatory. The food is a bit expensive but extremely tasty, and the staff are very friendly. }} * {{eat | name=Le Grec | alt= | url=https://legrec.fi/ | email=hello@legrec.fi | address=Rikhardinkatu 2 | lat=60.16602 | long= 24.94706 | directions= | phone=+358 40-632-6552 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=Tu–Th 14:00–23:00, F–Sa 14:00–00:00 | price=€50 | lastedit=2025-07-18 | content=A Greek restaurant. }} * {{eat | name=Havis | alt= | url=http://www.royalravintolat.com/havis/index_eng.asp | email= | address=Eteläranta 16 | lat=60.16656 | long= 24.95218 | directions=Trams 1, 1A and 2 | phone=+358 9 6869-5660 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=The successor of the legendary Havis Amanda and still the best upscale seafood restaurant in town. }} * {{eat | name=Olo | alt= | url=http://www.olo-restaurant.com | email= | address=Kasarmikatu 44 | lat=60.16626 | long=24.94748 | directions= | phone=+358 9 665-565 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=Combines North European ingredients into a modern Scandinavian cuisine while using seasons best ingredients available. }} * {{eat | name=Ora | alt= | url=https://orarestaurant.fi/en/ora-english/ | email=hello@orarestaurant.fi | address=Huvilakatu 28 | lat=60.15770 | long=24.94272 | directions=near the Eira Hospital | phone=+358 400-959-440 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=An atmospheric restaurant that serves top quality local food made from seasonal ingredients and wine. }} * {{eat | name=Palace Gourmet | alt= | url=http://www.palacerestaurant.fi/en | email=sales@palace.fi | address=Eteläranta 10 | lat=60.16524 | long=24.95239 | directions=10th Floor | phone=+358 9 1345-6715 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=W–Sa 18:00–24:00 | price= | content=Fine dining restaurant. Established in 1952, it got its second Michelin star in 2022. }} * {{eat | name=Ragu | alt= | url=https://www.ragu.fi/ | email=reservations@ragu.fi (last reservations at 21:30) | address=Ludviginkatu 3-5 | lat=60.16586 | long=24.94468 | directions= | phone=+358 9 596-659 (from 15:00) | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M–Sa 17:00–00:00 | price=Menu Ragu: €55–62; Menu Ludari (Chef´s Menu): €49–62 | content=A fine dining restaurant that serves innovative dishes and wines selected according to the season. }} * {{eat | name=Saaga | alt= | url=http://www.ravintolasaaga.fi/en/front-page.html | email= | address=Bulevardi 34 B | lat=60.16313 | long=24.93392 | directions= | phone=+358 9 7425-5544 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price=€50 for a full meal | content=Traditional [[Finnish Lapland|Lapp]] food in kitschy Lapp surroundings – reindeer horn chandeliers and the lot – but unlike some of the competition, they don't compromise on food quality. The octolingual menu runs the gamut from smoked elk to bear meatballs. Don't miss the buttermilk pancakes (''äkäset'') for dessert. }} * {{eat | name=Saslik | alt= | url=https://ravintolasaslik.fi/en/etusivu-english/ | email= | address=Neitsytpolku 12 | lat=60.15863 | long=24.94878 | directions= | phone=+358 9 7425-5500 | tollfree= | hours= | price=Meals €20–35, bear dishes €66–76 | content=Traditional Russian delicacies. Russian music and decor of old samovars, stained-glass windows and paintings. Try traditional blinis or Saslik's bear specialities. }} * {{eat | name=Skörd Freda | alt= | url=https://sk%C3%B6rd.fi/en/ | email=varaukset@skord.fi | address=Fredrikinkatu 37 | lat=60.16402 | long=24.93767 | directions= | phone=+358 50-337-6691 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M–Sa 17:00–00:00 | price=Menu €72–86 | content=Restaurant using seasonal ingredients. }} * {{eat | name=Särkänlinna | alt= | url=http://www.ravintolasarkanlinna.fi/en/ | email=sarkanlinna@palacekamp.fi | address=Särkänsaari island | lat=60.15055 | long=24.96673 | directions=Särkansaari island | phone=+358 9 1345-6756 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=Särkänlinna offers a Nordic cuisine. Provides a good premise for dinners for two to as well as weddings or private parties. Famous for its traditional crayfish parties. }}
==Drink== [[File:Helsinki waterfront from Tähtitornimäki.JPG|thumbnail|View from Tähtitorninmäki]]
===Cafés=== * {{drink | name=Cafe Succès | alt= | url= | email= | address=Korkeavuorenkatu 2 | lat=60.15962 | long= 24.94645 | directions= | phone=+358 9 633-414 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=This traditional cafe serves excellent delicacies. Famous for their enormous cinnamon rolls (''korvapuusti''), also available in '''Cafe Esplanad'''. }} * {{drink | name=Kakkugalleria | alt= | url=http://www.kakkugalleria.com | email= | address=Erottaja 7 | lat=60.16495 | long= 24.94426 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=French-type cafe in the Design Forum. Try the lovely Sacher cake. Take away is cheaper. }} * {{drink | name=Plootu Furniture | alt= | url=http://plootu.fi | email= | address=Iso Roobertinkatu 32 | lat=60.162538 | long=24.939736 | directions=Trams 1 and 3 stop at Iso Roobertinkatu | phone=+358 44-988-7589 (mobile) | tollfree= | fax= | hours=| price= | lastedit=2018-03-09 | content=The café and furniture shop Plootu offers a great tea selection (served in a 600ml/1000ml presso pan), smoothies, salads, coffee and pho soup. An atmospheric and fun little coffee shop where everything you dine or drink coffee on is on sale. }}
===Alcohol===
* {{drink | name=Adler Wine House | alt= | url=https://adlerfelt.fi/en/adler-house/ | email= | address=Suomenlinna B 2 | lat=60.14476 | long=24.98615 | directions= | phone=+358 41-317-0998 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=Su–M 12:00–18:00, Tu–Sa 12:00–22:00 | price= | content=A summer wine bar open from the end of May until the beginning of September. }} * {{drink | name=Ahjo | alt= | url= | email= | address=Bulevardi 2 | lat=60.16620 | long=24.94290 | directions=''Klaus K'' | phone=+358 20-770-4711 | tollfree= | fax= | hours=M-Sa | price=Drinks €6–8 | content=Named after the forge where the mythical Sampo of the Kalevala was made, this is a slick modern bar-lounge with two sides to it: a pure white space as you enter, with a bar counter and sofas, and a darker back room with nooks and crannies for a quieter chat. Try the drink ''Ahjotonic''. }} * {{drink | name=Black Door | alt= | url=http://www.blackdoor.fi | email= | address=Iso Roobertinkatu 1 | lat=60.16419 | long=24.94384 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=English pub. Weekdays are relaxed, weekends have live DJs and a full bar. A place to go for quality beers, ales, ciders and whisky. }} * {{drink | name=Erottaja Bar | alt= | url= | email= | address=Erottajankatu 15–17 | lat= 60.16599 | long= 24.94418 | directions= | phone=+358 9 611-196 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | content=A small, consciously crude bar, that used to be one of the primary hipster hangouts in central Helsinki. The bar is now all but deserted by the trendy crowd, and the music turned into the usual fare of hit-list pop, but on the upside the service is friendly and there is ample sitting room at the tables. }} * {{drink | name=Kaarle XII| alt= | url=http://www.kaarle.com | email= | address=Kasarmikatu 40 | lat=60.16563 | long=24.94761 | directions= | phone=+358 9 612-9990 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= Th–Sa 22:00–04:00 | price= | content=A Helsinki institution better known as ''Kalle'', this former church hasn't had a renovation in years and really needs one. It still continues to pack in a hard-partying thirty-something crowd, especially on Thursdays. Six bars (all small), playing top-40 tunes, rock and Finnish pop. The last of the bars has a dance floor and gets particularly packed, with people dancing on the tables. Minimum age 24. }}
==Sleep== [[File:Palace Hotel, Helsinki, East view 20100825 1.jpg|thumbnail|Palace no longer functions as a hotel, but the restaurant is open and it is a major landmark]]
===Budget=== * {{sleep | name=Hostel Suomenlinna | alt= | url=https://www.hostelhelsinki.fi/en | email= | address=Suomenlinna C 9 | lat=60.14854 | long=24.98454 | directions=ferry connection from Market Square | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | checkin= | checkout= | price= | content=All year open hostel located at the Suomenlinna sea fortress. Great for a quick escape from the city. The ferry runs from 6AM to 2AM so you are not totally cut off. }} * {{sleep | name=Hostel Diana Park | alt= | url=http://www.dianapark.fi | email= | address=Uudenmaankatu 9 | lat=60.16489 | long=24.94168 | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | checkin= | checkout= | price=€27 for a dorm bed | content=A small, clean, and friendly hostel with a central location. }}
===Mid-range=== * {{sleep | name=Hotel Anna | alt= | url=https://www.hotelanna.fi/?lang=en | email=info@hotelanna.fi | address=Annankatu 1 | lat=60.162920 | long=24.942720 | directions= | phone=+358 9 616-621 | tollfree= | checkin= | checkout= | price=rates from €73 | image=Hotel Anna.JPG | lastedit=2026-02-10 | content=A hotel owned by the Evangelical Free Church of Finland (EFCF). }}
===Splurge=== * {{sleep | name=Klaus K | url=http://www.klauskhotel.com | email= | address=Bulevardi 2 | lat= 60.16623 | long= 24.94299 | directions= | phone=+358 20-770-4700 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price=From €115 | checkin= | checkout= | content=Helsinki's first boutique hotel, although they prefer the term "personal contemporary hotel". Rooms range from the small Passion & Mystical types to the aptly named Envy Plus. Central location, funky styling and reasonable prices make this a winner. }} * {{sleep | name=Hotel Haven | url=http://www.hotelhaven.fi/en | email= | address=Unioninkatu 17 | lat=60.16665 | long=24.95142 | directions= | phone=+358 9 681-930 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price=From €169 | checkin= | checkout= | content=Hotel Haven, Finland’s first member of the Small Luxury Hotels of the World, is designed to provide homely warmth, exclusive comfort and high-quality services for the discerning guest. }} * {{sleep | name=Sokos Hotel Albert | alt= | url=https://www.sokoshotels.fi/en/helsinki/sokos-hotel-albert | email=albert.helsinki@sokoshotels.fi | address=Albertinkatu 30 |lat=60.16278 | long=24.93524 | directions= | phone=+358 20-123-4638 | tollfree= | fax=+358 20-123-4639 | checkin= | checkout= | price= | lastedit=2015-09-16 | content= }}
